Uses of Class
harrygpotter.tombola.tombolalib.TAwardList

  • Uses of TAwardList in harrygpotter.tombola.tombolalib

    Methods in harrygpotter.tombola.tombolalib that return TAwardList 
    Modifier and Type Method Description
    TAwardList TGame.getAwardList()
    Return the complete list of award objects currently used by this game.
    static TAwardList TAwardList.getSimpleDoubleAwardList()
    Helper static method providing a sample, standard award list containing a two prizes (that is, "PRIMO" and "SECONDO") for each values from AMBO to QUINTINA and then TOMBOLA.
    static TAwardList TAwardList.getSimpleSingleAwardList()
    Helper static method providing a sample, standard award list containing a single prize for values from AMBO to QUINTINA and then TOMBOLA.
    Methods in harrygpotter.tombola.tombolalib with parameters of type TAwardList 
    Modifier and Type Method Description
    void TGame.setAwardList​(TAwardList awards)
    Set the (previously prepared, see TAwardList) list of awards that will be available during the game. As usual, even this setter method can be invoked only during the INITIALIZING status of the tombola game object.
